description: I met an interesting guy recently. He called me a few days before christmas and was desperate for help. When I came there I noticed that he had a rather nice apartment. Clearly a girl was taking care of it to keep it clean and tidy. However, the guy and his girlfriend recently lost their jobs and made some fresh debts. Not a fortune - basically a few rents and a mobile provider. But as they didn´t pay the rent for three months they were about to loose the apartment. And that indeed would be tough. So I wanted to help while I was in a comfortable position as well. The 25 000 CZK he was asking for I could easily afford. On the other hand he couldn´t afford to reject my offer so close to get evicted. And indeed this cutie undressed faster than expected...
title: Debt Dandy 120
